						<summary>Begins with the historical introduction <foreign>Samastajagadādhāra</foreign>, etc. Records a royal order making a tax-free <foreign>dēvadāna</foreign> endowment of the village Nallūr to the temple of Nalla-Nāyaṉār for the maintenance of a service in the name of the king and for the <supplied reason="subaudible">expenses of</supplied> the festival in the month of Tai.</summary>
